{"tid":108271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圖／好害羞！稀有生物「陰莖蛇」曝光　讓你臉紅心狂跳","createTime":"2017-02-05T06:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T17:02:30.000Z","uid":3189,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab4fcfcfb6535740133a85f08f31a171930b6bf","tid":108271,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:40:13.000Z","msg":"2016/01/08 16:05:00<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n世界上無奇不有！2011年生物學家發現的罕見生物「陰莖蛇」（Penis snake），近日引起網友熱烈討論。這種生物被發現於巴西亞馬遜河支流的一座發電廠附近，奇特的樣貌就像男性的生殖器官，讓生物學家、網友留下深刻印象，紛紛表示「還是魯蛇最猛啦」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2016/01/08/421497-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F01%2F08%2F421497-XXL.jpg&h=ec2df9d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陰莖蛇（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2016/01/08/421501-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F01%2F08%2F421501-XXL.jpg&h=198ab7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陰莖蛇（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n長相奇特的「陰莖蛇」是由生物學家Julian Tupan發現，他認為這生物可能是伊氏真蚓（Atretochoana eiselti），因為這生物只有外觀長得像蛇，但它不屬於爬蟲類，反而更接近兩棲類。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2016/01/08/421502-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F01%2F08%2F421502-XXL.jpg&h=6e14655e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陰莖蛇（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nTupan認為陰莖蛇幾乎沒有視力功能，主要靠嗅覺來分辨情況，另外可能是透過皮膚來呼吸，並且主要以小魚或是蚯蚓為食，但學界目前對於此生物的了解還不夠充足。看到此奇異外形的生物，網友認為「如果有X皮的話那就更像」、「開眼界了」！（整理：實習編輯林緯平）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=reMTd5d5D3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DreMTd5d5D3o&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b9dacd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=reMTd5d5D3o</a><br />\n<br />\n來源 : <a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=117151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D117151&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=80fd26e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D117151&h=6eca8501\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=117151</a>"},{"pid":"97cdfaae51b1012494f2030c090b6048e7a28f3a","tid":108271,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4be052c054fb7a943eac89ed8c0dbadae6fc809","tid":108271,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"BAM"},{"pid":"30b9692cedd06b6eb37abe7b22faf50e553b1ec7","tid":108271,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"以為賓周生得似蛇就唔洗bam?"},{"pid":"a41b2e7971ad8eed744f7b702b3eafc693b55e43","tid":108271,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"撚樣"},{"pid":"bc24da30b21e2c3ee8769be7d30191601c6eba0c","tid":108271,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"Bam <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f64b5258ece827d68ed051d82cc679b83bb917","tid":108271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"這裏不是高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556a3fe64c9419fa09c2e0b90fa9eb271758ed08","tid":108271,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為賓周生得似蛇就唔洗bam?</blockquote><br />\n咪撚係"},{"pid":"9770ec9a2c0c41cf78b43079585a24f4373ddb34","tid":108271,"uid":14905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:01